                        "text": "<p>See our instructions <a href=\"https://mwlbride.com/pages/measurement-guide\" title=\"/pages/measurement-guide\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>here</em></span></a> on how to measure yourself. Please reach out to<span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>hello@mwlbride.com</em></span> if you have any further questions.</p>",
